---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const pageTitle = "Freelance MERN Developer in Valsad | Nikhil";
const pageDescription = "Need a developer in Valsad? I build MERN apps, AI automation, and agentic systems for startups and local businesses across Gujarat.";
const pageKeywords = "developer in Valsad, MERN developer Valsad, AI developer Valsad, freelance full stack developer Gujarat, agentic AI developer";

const serviceSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  serviceType: "Freelance Full Stack and AI Development",
  areaServed: "Valsad, Gujarat, India",
  provider: {
    "@type": "Person",
    name: "Nikhil Yagik",
    url: "https://nikhilyagik.dev/developer-in-valsad"
  },
  description: pageDescription
};
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} keywords={pageKeywords} image="/logo.png">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="bg-white min-h-screen pt-28 pb-20 px-4">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wide text-slate-500 uppercase mb-4">Valsad Local Development Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6">Freelance Full Stack and AI Developer in Valsad</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Valsad businesses are moving quickly toward digital-first operations, and the biggest challenge is usually execution.
        Ideas are clear, but building a reliable product takes technical depth, consistency, and speed.
        I help founders and growing teams in Valsad build modern web products and practical AI systems that solve real business problems.
        My work combines full stack MERN development with agentic AI workflows, so you can launch faster without managing multiple vendors.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        If you are searching for a freelance MERN developer in Valsad, or an AI developer who can integrate intelligent features into existing applications,
        I can support both new builds and ongoing improvements.
        I focus on production-ready delivery: clean architecture, secure APIs, maintainable code, and communication that keeps the project on track.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">What I Offer to Clients in Valsad</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        My core service is end-to-end software delivery.
        I design and build frontend interfaces in React and Astro, backend services in Node.js and Express,
        and data layers in MongoDB and PostgreSQL depending on scale and workload.
        For businesses that need operational efficiency, I add AI capabilities using LangGraph and RAG pipelines,
        allowing teams to automate routine tasks and retrieve business information instantly.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Every Valsad business has different needs.
        Some want conversion-focused websites and dashboards.
        Others need appointment flows, partner onboarding systems, custom admin portals, or AI-assisted support flows.
        I work from your business process, not from a generic template, which means your product is easier to use and easier to scale.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2 mb-10">
        <li>Custom web app development using MERN and modern UI architecture</li>
        <li>Backend APIs, authentication, role-based access, and workflow logic</li>
        <li>AI assistants and document intelligence using RAG and LLMs</li>
        <li>Agentic AI automation with LangGraph for multi-step tasks</li>
        <li>Performance optimization, deployment, and ongoing improvements</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Real Projects: Servielliance, TimeCapsule, and Agentic Systems</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        The best way to judge a developer is by shipped systems.
        Servielliance is one of my key projects, a service marketplace platform with role-based flows,
        booking management, and strong backend architecture.
        It reflects how I approach real production complexity: clear user journeys, scalable APIs,
        and practical decisions for long-term maintainability.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        TimeCapsule is another example that shows my AI plus product integration skills.
        Users create and retrieve timestamped reminders through natural language interaction,
        while the system handles scheduling logic and contextual retrieval behind the scenes.
        This is relevant for many Valsad businesses that need intelligent automation but still want reliable, predictable behavior.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        I have also built agentic AI pipelines using LangGraph, including workflow routing,
        retrieval steps, and content orchestration.
        These systems are useful for teams that want AI to complete real tasks, not just respond with generic chat output.
        If your business needs automation with structure and accountability, this approach works.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Why Work With Me as Your Valsad Developer</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        One reason clients choose me is ownership.
        I do not just deliver isolated screens or scripts.
        I treat the project as a full product with user flow, technical architecture, deployment stability, and future iteration in mind.
        This avoids fragmentation and keeps your product coherent as requirements evolve.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Another reason is communication clarity.
        You get milestone planning, practical technical decisions, and regular updates without unnecessary complexity.
        I keep timelines realistic, surface trade-offs early, and focus on business outcomes instead of feature bloat.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        For Valsad and nearby areas, local context also matters.
        Shared time zone and regional understanding make it easier to collaborate quickly, discuss priorities,
        and adapt solutions to your market realities.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">How We Can Start</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Most projects begin with a short discovery discussion where we define your objective,
        current blockers, and preferred timeline.
        I then provide a practical implementation plan with phases and deliverables,
        so you can make a clear decision before development starts.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        I am available for project-based builds and long-term freelance support.
        If you need a full stack developer in Valsad, a MERN engineer for your platform,
        or an AI developer in Gujarat for automation and intelligent workflows,
        I would be happy to discuss your goals.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions in Valsad</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can you improve an existing app instead of building from scratch?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Yes. Many Valsad clients approach me with products that need performance fixes,
        feature expansion, or cleaner architecture.
        I can audit the current codebase, identify bottlenecks, and implement a phased upgrade path
        so your team gets improvements without unnecessary downtime.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Do you support AI automation for local workflows?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Yes. I build AI workflows that automate repetitive business processes,
        such as document lookup, response drafting, content workflows, and process routing.
        The key focus is reliability and business fit,
        so your team can depend on the automation in daily operations.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What engagement model do you offer?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        I work on project-based contracts and ongoing freelance partnerships.
        If you need a developer for a defined scope, we can run milestone delivery.
        If you need continuous product growth, we can set up monthly execution cycles with priority planning.
      </p>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Build Your Next Product with Confidence</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Lets turn your product idea or operational challenge into a clean, scalable system that your business can depend on.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/#contact" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-900 text-white font-medium hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">Hire Me</a>
          <a href="/#projects" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-900 font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">See Project Work</a>
          <a href="/developer-in-vapi" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-900 font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">Vapi Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(serviceSchema)} />
</MainLayout>
